OL,3,CMen accused of taking part in violent
OL,4,Cdisorder in Hartlepool appear in court
OL,6,FA man cried in court as he and his
OL,7,Fpartner admitted joining in the
OL,8,Fdisorder that broke out in Hartlepool
OL,9,Fon Wednesday night.
OL,11,FSteven Mailen, 54, of Elliott Street,
OL,12,FHartlepool, and Ryan Sheers, 28, of
OL,13,FPowlett Street, each admitted a single
OL,14,Fcharge of violent disorder during a
OL,15,Fseries of hearings for seven
OL,16,Fdefendants at Teesside Magistrates'
OL,17,FCourt.
