OL,3,CMen accused of taking part in violent
OL,4,Cdisorder in Hartlepool appear in court
OL,6,FThe defendants, who have no previous
OL,7,Fconvictions, were granted bail by
OL,8,FDistrict Judge Helen Cousins to appear
OL,9,Fbefore Teesside Crown Court for
OL,10,Fsentencing on September 2.
OL,12,FSheers, formerly a McDonalds worker,
OL,13,Fwas emotional and said: "Thank you
OL,14,Fjudge, thank you."
OL,16,FThe pair covered their faces as they
OL,17,Fleft court.
OL,19,FWhen asked why they got involved,
OL,20,FSheers replied: "Didn't get involved
OL,21,Fin nothing."
